# Docker auto-deploy (SkyScan)

When changes affect Docker images, entrypoints, Dockerfiles, `docker-compose.yaml`, or service configs used by compose (`video-gateway.env`, `cot-bridge.env`, `.env` keys consumed by services), run from the repo root **before finishing the turn**:

```bash
docker compose build && docker compose up -d
```

Recreate services so new images and env files are picked up. **Do not prompt** the user for permission to run deploy commands for this project.
